title: Chermoula-Spiced Honey Beef Rump with Sesame Roast Root Veggie Toss & Garlic Yoghurt
description: Enjoy the tastes of this warming dinner that’s sure to transport your taste buds. In one bite you’ll be hit with spiced succulent beef rump drizzled in honey, roasted veggies and punchy garlic yoghurt. Everyone will want seconds!

